/*! \fn void E_DIAG_SendAndCompareParamString(diagRequest *aDiagReq, char aParameterName[], char aStringToCompareWithParam[])
*  \brief Function that will send the request, get the Symbolic text of a parameter and compare it with the specified string. NOTE: If parameter does not have a Symbol text defined in .cdd or .pdx, the numeric value will be compared instead.
*  \param[in]  aDiagReq 		                - Diagnostic request.
*  \param[in]  aParameterName 	            - The parameter name of the diagnostic request (ex: "P2s_CAN_ECU_max").
